  "how_to_use": "❓ How to use",
  "help_step1_title": "1️⃣ First login",
  "help_step1_text": "If you were given a phone and password — enter them on the login screen. If you don't have an account yet — click «Register», enter your name, phone and create a password.",
  "help_step2_title": "2️⃣ Connect Telegram",
  "help_step2_text": "After logging in, click the blue banner «📱 Connect notifications» at the top. The bot @DispetcherPro_bot will open — send your phone number. You will now receive notifications about new shifts and payments.",
  "help_step3_title": "3️⃣ Shift invitation",
  "help_step3_text": "When a dispatcher assigns you to a shift — it will appear in the list marked «📞 Invitation». Click ✅ Accept to accept, or ❌ Decline if you can't. You can decline up to 3 hours before the start.",
  "help_step4_title": "4️⃣ Starting work",
  "help_step4_text": "On the shift day, the ▶️ «Start work» button will appear. Click it when you actually start. The time will be recorded automatically.",
  "help_step5_title": "5️⃣ Ending work",
  "help_step5_text": "When finished — click ⏹ «End work». Hours and payment amount will be calculated automatically based on your rate.",
  "help_step6_title": "6️⃣ Payment",
  "help_step6_text": "The dispatcher marks the payment. When the shift status is «✅ Paid» — you can receive the money. The amount due is shown at the top of the page.",
  "help_step7_title": "💡 Forgot password?",
  "help_step7_text": "On the login screen click «Forgot password?» — a new password will be sent to Telegram. If Telegram is not linked — contact your dispatcher.",
  "client_help_title": "📖 Client guide",
  "client_help_1_title": "1️⃣ New order",
  "client_help_1_text": "Click the green «➕ New order» button on the main page. Fill in the form: specify service type, date, time, number of workers and object address. After submitting, all dispatchers in your city will be notified. The first responding dispatcher will take the order.",
  "client_help_2_title": "2️⃣ Order status",
  "client_help_2_text": "After creation, the order has «Pending» status. When a dispatcher accepts the order, the status changes to «In progress» and worker search begins. You will see confirmed workers in real time.",
  "client_help_3_title": "3️⃣ Connect Telegram",
  "client_help_3_text": "After logging in, click the blue banner «📱 Connect notifications» at the top. The bot @DispetcherPro_bot will open — send your phone number. You will receive notifications about order status and invoices.",
  "client_help_4_title": "4️⃣ «💰 Payments» tab",
  "client_help_4_text": "When an invoice arrives — it appears here. Click «Pay» and upload a receipt photo or transfer screenshot.",
  "client_help_5_title": "5️⃣ «📊 Analytics» tab",
  "client_help_5_text": "Monthly summary: hours worked, total amount, paid amount and remaining debt.",
  "client_help_6_title": "📞 Contact",
  "client_help_6_text": "For any questions, contact your dispatcher.",
